    "description_long": "This object depicts a lush, green graveyard set within an urban park-like environment. The area is dotted with mature trees, grassy lawns, and a scattering of gravestones and monuments, some of which are upright headstones and others are flat markers. In one view, a domed mausoleum or chapel constructed from brick or stone is visible, adding architectural interest to the scene. The sky is bright and partly cloudy, casting natural light over the landscape. The graveyard is tranquil, with pathways winding through the grass and between the graves, and there are no visible fences or gates enclosing the area.",
